title: batches_outstanding == 0 in dataloader during iteration
body_html:
• PyTorch or Caffe2: Pytorch
  • OS: ubuntu16.04
  • PyTorch version: 0.3.1
  • How you installed PyTorch (conda, pip, source): pip
  • Python version: 3.6
  • CUDA/cuDNN version: cuda8.0

I got this error during iteration:

~/anaconda3/lib/python3.6/site-packages/torch/utils/data/dataloader.py in __next__(self)
    269         if self.batches_outstanding == 0:
    270             self._shutdown_workers()
--> 271             raise StopIteration
    272 
    273         while True:

StopIteration:

Is anybody can help?
